data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS HAVE BEEN RECEIVED. NEW OR REVISED OFFERS DUE BY 9PM ON MONDAY, NOVEMBER 20TH. SELLERS WILL MAKE A DECISION ON TUESDAY. Excellent curb appeal and a beautifully maintained lot, boasting a new privacy fence, add to the desire of this home nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. Perfect location close to downtown White Bear Lake, parks, schools, and restaurants. Updates that the sellers have done in the past 8 yrs include Furnace & AC, Electrical Panel, Fencing, Recessed Lighting, SS Appliances, Quartz Countertops in Kitchen and Lining the Sewer Line to the Street. Upper bedroom windows (one in each room) have been replaced. Excellent storage in the lower basement area off of the family room & kitchen, and in 12x10 yard shed.  Love where you live!  Quick closing possible
